      • hasEmbedding

        Boolean hasEmbedding(GraphWithCandidates graph,
                     String query)
        Returns true, if the graph contains the pattern. This should be much faster than findEmbeddings, because early aborting is possible.
        Parameters:
        graph - a graph with its vertices and edges as well as their candidates
        query - a query string
        Returns:
        true, if the graph contains an instance of the pattern
